{"tid":1455263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叫人果啲人一係抬啲人走，一係一齊留","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T09:08:17.000Z","uid":295630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3ee77029b08d1051bce311efedff88c4145ac9","tid":1455263,"uid":295630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:50:12.000Z","msg":"叫完人走，散左一堆，留低果啲就俾人打。你想走，唔該逐個逐個拖人走，呢啲先叫不割蓆"},{"pid":"8ccb3385e649e3558894ca4b0ca035df8cf04a24","tid":1455263,"uid":165246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:50:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">走呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留既人除左想坐監之外我都諗唔到點解要留</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日所有航班已取消!取消！取消！取消！取消！<br />\n機場圍捕無路走！<br />\n所有手足請即散<br />\n記得係一齊散！一齊散！一齊散！<br />\n唔好落單！<br />\n擇日再戰<br />\n切實執行不被捕原則！<br />\n仲有咩好留呀 叫你留個d 自己諗下係咪鬼啦<br />\n仲有咩好留呀<br />\n仲有咩好留先<br />\n點解仲要留係到</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngYyt3j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngYyt3j.png&h=916dd304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSMoRgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSMoRgG.png&h=734c1f44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYUBrP8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYUBrP8.png&h=f9aef586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"979ff860c75a43018e2cc638fdb16546a7463321","tid":1455263,"uid":178042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"係走既 一齊走 唔好走部分<br />\n剩低既會仆晒街<br />\n理性講點解走"},{"pid":"b72dbeebbce17b3d74a49c6f7496e97371d02821","tid":1455263,"uid":255013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"今次一定要走<br />\n首先，狗已經有曬準備，禁區佈防，旗手防暴齊曬<br />\n然後，地理問題，如果狗要圍捕真係無路可走<br />\n最後，手足冇gear！！！！！唔可以打冇準備嘅仗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場返工嘅朋友親見到<br />\n有大量警察運左啲嘢入禁區<br />\n要走嘅話暫時s1巴士小人排<br />\n個站係的士站隔離<br />\n快啲通知你係機場嘅朋友"},{"pid":"022e5ac7f5452e994bc94a7c82b79bd198562fd7","tid":1455263,"uid":255013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:08:17.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}